snippet.title: Rivals of Aether II Deep Dive:  Launch Features
snippet.description:
Let's talk about launch features in Rivals II! Join studio lead Dan Fornace for the first video in our three part Deep Dive series. Make sure to tune in next week for parts 2 and 3, as well as an open Q&A where we answer all of your burning questions.

Support the game by wishlisting Rivals of Aether II on steam at https://rivals2.com/wishlist
